HEADWORD: Insalubrity
<hw>In`sa*lu"bri*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>insalubrite</ets>.]</ety> <def>Unhealthfulness; unwholesomeness;
